d/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">yamoo9 gitbook CSS grid</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">grid-template</code> 에서 <code class=\"language-text\">repeat()</code>은 IE 지원안함. IE를 위한 grid project kit 에서 다른 방식으로 가능하게 할 수도…</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2>다섯 번째 시간</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">transform</code> 속성의 <code class=\"language-text\">rotate()</code>가 돌아가는 기준은 항상 센터다.</li>\n<li>오늘의 예제에서 했던 속성이나 method들 숙련되게 연습.</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"12. HTML&CSS TIL","summary":"","date":"2021.08.24.","categories":["HTML","CSS"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.8018018018018018,"src":"/static/c573ae301c128e4304d611365b135061/1cc83/HTMLCSS.jpg","srcSet":"/static/c573ae301c128e4304d611365b135061/ae57a/HTMLCSS.jpg 200w,\n/static/c573ae301c128e4304d611365b135061/1cc83/HTMLCSS.jpg 302w","srcWebp":"/static/c573ae301c128e4304d611365b135061/3e60d/HTMLCSS.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/c573ae301c128e4304d611365b135061/8444f/HTMLCSS.webp 200w,\n/static/c573ae301c128e4304d611365b135061/3e60d/HTMLCSS.webp 302w","sizes":"(max-width: 302px) 100vw, 302px"}},"publicURL":"/static/c573ae301c128e4304d611365b135061/HTMLCSS.jpg"}}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/HTML_CSS/0824/HTML&CSS_0824/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}